---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy - dustinlanders.com">
  <article class="legal-page">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: April 1, 2026</p>

    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>
      This privacy policy describes how Dustin Landers ("I", "me") collects, uses, and protects
      information in connection with SMS/MMS messaging services operated through this phone number.
    </p>

    <h2>Information Collected</h2>
    <p>
      When you communicate with me via SMS/MMS, the following information may be collected:
      your phone number, the content of messages you send and receive, and message timestamps.
    </p>

    <h2>How Information Is Used</h2>
    <p>
      Your information is used solely for the purpose of sending and receiving personal
      notifications and group messages. Messages may be sent by an AI assistant (Claude)
      on my behalf to coordinate plans, send reminders, and check in with contacts.
    </p>

    <h2>Information Sharing</h2>
    <p>
      Your personal information is not sold, rented, or shared with third parties for
      marketing purposes. Message data may be processed by Twilio (the messaging platform
      provider) and Anthropic (the AI assistant provider) in order to deliver the service.
    </p>

    <h2>Data Retention</h2>
    <p>
      Message data is retained only as long as necessary to provide the service.
      You may request deletion of your data at any time by contacting me directly.
    </p>

    <h2>Opting Out</h2>
    <p>
      You can opt out of receiving messages at any time by replying STOP to any message.
      You may also contact me directly to be removed from messaging.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions about this privacy policy, contact me at
      <a href="mailto:dustin.landers@gmail.com">dustin.landers@gmail.com</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .legal-page h1 {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .legal-page h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .last-updated {
    color: #888;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
</style>
